<li>\n              <span><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/\">WORK STYLE</a></span>\n              <ul class=\"lower\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/suzaki/\">須﨑 久美子</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/taguchi/\">田口 晴基</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/nakashima/\">中島 知子</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer-nav-wrap\">\n          <!--<ul class=\"nav-item\">\n            <li>\n              <span><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/\">WORK STYLE</a></span>\n              <ul class=\"lower\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/suzaki/\">須﨑 久美子</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/taguchi/\">田口 晴基</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/work_style/nakashima/\">中島 知子</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </li>\n          </ul> -->\n          <ul class=\"nav-item\">\n            <li>\n              <span><a href=\"/recruit_info/events/\">EVENT</a></span>\n              <ul class=\"lower\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/events/\">イベント情報</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/events/\">イベントレポート</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n          <ul class=\"nav-item\">\n            <li><span><a href=\"/recruit_info/recruit/\">RECRUIT</a></span></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer-proof\">\n          <div class=\"proof-item\">\n            <div><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/common/jpx_prime.png\" alt=\"東京証券取引所 プライム市場、証券コード4763\"></div>\n            <span>当サイトは株式会社クリーク･アンド･リバー社（東京証券取引所 プライム市場、証券コード4763）が運営しています。</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"proof-item\">\n            <div><a href=\"http://privacymark.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Opens in a new window\" class=\"mt-10 pmark-link\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/common/logo_privacy.png\" alt=\"プライバシーマーク\"></a></div>\n            <span>当社は、一般財団法人日本情報経済社会推進協会（JIPDEC）より「プライバシーマーク」の付与認定を受けています。</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"pagetop\"><a href=\"#pagetop\">ページトップへ</a></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\n    <div class=\"l-inner\">\n      <ul class=\"sub-nav\">\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.cri.co.jp/\">コーポレートサイト</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/recruit_info/\">TOPへ</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.cri.co.jp/policy/\">サイトポリシー</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.cri.co.jp/privacy/\">個人情報の保護について</a></li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"copy-right\">&copy;CREEK & RIVER Co., Ltd.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n</div>\n\n<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/js/slick/slick.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/js/scripts.js\"></script>\n\n<script>\n    if(window.location.origin==\"\"){\n    \n  \n    $(\"img\").each(function(){\n        $(this).prop('src', function () { return this.src.replace('www.cri.co.jp','admin-dev.cri.co.jp'); })\n    })\n  \n      $(\"a\").each(function(){\n           $(this).attr('href', $(this).attr('href').replace('www.cri.co.jp','admin-dev.cri.co.jp'));\n      })\n}\n    if(window.location.origin==\"https://www.cri.co.jp\"){\n    \n  \n    $(\"img\").each(function(){\n        $(this).prop('src', function () { return this.src.replace('admin-dev.cri.co.jp','www.cri.co.jp'); })\n    })\n  \n      $(\"a\").each(function(){\n           $(this).attr('href', $(this).attr('href').replace('admin-dev.cri.co.jp','www.cri.co.jp'));\n      })\n}\n</script>\n<script>\n    if (window.location.origin.includes(\"admin\")){\n    \t$('article').find('img').each(function(){\n        \tlet url = $(this).attr('src');\n        \turl = url.replace('https://www.cri.co.jp', '');\n            $(this).attr('src', url);\n    \t});\n    }\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n\n","finalUrl":"https://www.cri.co.jp/recruit_info/events/info/2027agent_work.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T22:44:30.941Z"}